{"tid":1512973,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"612到依家睇咁多時事評論員, 最準果個真係明居正","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:28:03.000Z","uid":67294,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa74deaab55152b8e07fffe920d799334ccea9e","tid":1512973,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"係&quot;年代向錢看&quot;認識明居正, 首先發覺係佢對中共政治架構好熟悉唔係9up而開始留意<br />\n之後發覺佢預測好多都中哂<br />\n<br />\n1. 611預言香港茉莉花革命開始-&gt;依家大家都叫時代革命<br />\n2. G20特朗普唔會出口幫香港<br />\n3. 中共唔會出解放軍, 最多會搞軍演玩恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n佢最近露面係8月21號, 預言林鄭可能用緊急法叫中共派武警入場<br />\n前幾日林鄭即刻就話唔排除出緊急法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家差唔多全部都中哂, 有啲佢講既我諗大家要留意返<br />\n佢話香港會大搜捕, 佢仲斷言話可能會捉過萬個都有可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共唔會拖到十月一國慶, 因為佢要以時間執手尾, 即係中共Set左九月頭就係deadline<br />\n最後最重要係, 今次運動連佢都唔知結局係點, 所以大家唔好再話咩輸咩輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e56cd165b8ca82aad3852e3300530984f03b58","tid":1512973,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2LZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=571b1cb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ2LZ6li1RkmcN